:::Sideswipe/Torca/Ratchet/Sky Lynx:::

::Sideswipe destroys the missle, but gets hit by the grenade, blowing him 
backwards.  he retaliates and fires 13 shots and 1 missle at Double Punch and 
12 shots and 1 missle at Ares::
~~~~~
::Torca destroys the missle, but gets hit by the stinger missles.  he fires 
13 explosive shells at Double Punch and 12 at Injector::
~~~~~
::Ratchet gets hit by 2 ion disks and both optic blasts.  He fires 15 shots 
from one gun and 1 tusk missle at Manterror, and 15 shots from the other gun 
and 1 tusk missle at Bumblebee::
~~~~~
::Sky Lynx got hit by three of the blasts.  He ifred 2 missles from each gun 
at Sixshot::
